PrecisSetting apart, for the use and benefit of the BEARDY'S AND OKEMASIS BAND, of land in Saskatchewan, as follows: some 25 hectares, mines and minerals included, as an addition to Beardy's and Okemasis Indian Reserve No. 96 & 97-A, and some 172 hectares, mines and minerals included, as an addition to its Reserve No. 96 & 97-B, together with the mines and minerals existing within another 1.619 hectares of land.
